			<h4><a id="comment_link_64341411" name="comment_link_64341411" href="//news.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23267601&amp;cid=64341411" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64341411)" >It's not just about the greenhouse effect</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64341411" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64341411); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>1</a>)</span></h4>
